Class RegkeyAuditedPermissionsItem

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OvalObject

    public class RegkeyAuditedPermissionsItem
extends ItemType
    This item stores the audited access rights of a registry key that a system access control list (SACL) structure grants to a specified trustee.
